val age_1 = user_fields.map(fields => (fields(0),fields(1).toInt)).filter(line => (line._2 <= 9))
val id_30 = rating_data.map(array => (array(0),array(1))).filter(line => (line._1 == "30")).toDF().show

val id_movie = rating_data.map(fields => (fields(0).toInt,fields(1).toInt))
val id_rate = rating_data.map(fields => (fields(0).toInt,fields(2).toDouble))
val id_gender = user_fields.map(array => (array(0).toInt,array(2)))
val id_mrg = id_movie.join(id_gender).join(id_rate).map(line => (line._1,line._2._1._1,line._2._1._2,line._2._2))
//female
val id_mrg_f = id_mrg.filter(line => (line._3 == "F")).map(array => (array._2,array._4))
val id_mrg_f_size = id_mrg_f.groupByKey().map(line=>(line._1,line._2.size))
val id_mrg_f_sum = id_mrg_f.reduceByKey(_+_)
val id_mrg_f_avg = id_mrg_f_size.join(id_mrg_f_sum).map(line=>(line._1,(line._2._2/line._2._1).formatted("%.4f").toDouble))
//male
val id_mrg_m = id_mrg.filter(line => (line._3 == "M")).map(array => (array._2,array._4))
val id_mrg_m_size = id_mrg_m.groupByKey().map(line=>(line._1,line._2.size))
val id_mrg_m_sum = id_mrg_m.reduceByKey(_+_)
val id_mrg_m_avg = id_mrg_m_size.join(id_mrg_m_sum).map(line=>(line._1,(line._2._2/line._2._1).formatted("%.4f").toDouble))
//male and female :id
val total_id = id_mrg_f_avg.join(id_mrg_m_avg)
// .map(line=>(line._1, line._2._1, line._2._2,Math.abs(line._2._1-line._2._2)))
val total_name = movie_name.join(total_id).map(line=>(line._2._1, line._2._2._1, line._2._2._2,Math.abs(line._2._2._1-line._2._2._2).formatted("%.4f").toDouble)).sortBy(_._4,false)
